        "LocalizationKey": "Herbs_And_Fungi_OilPress_CardDescription",
        "DefaultText": "A mechanical oil press for extracting oil. Open the Recipes tab to press hemp seeds, a truffle, or fresh herbs into oil."
    },
    "CardHelpSection": {
        "ParentObjectID": "herbs_fungi_oil_press",
        "LocalizationKey": "Herbs_And_Fungi_OilPress_CardHelpSection",
        "DefaultText": "<b>How to Use:</b>\n• Open the <b>Recipes</b> tab on the press\n• Press Hemp Seeds (3 seeds + bowl), Press Truffle (1 truffle + bowl), or press fresh herbs (fairyweed, hemp flower, appleweed, frostleaf + bowl)\n• Each recipe consumes the ingredients and produces 1 bowl of oil\n\n<b>Herbal oils</b> give the same calming/mood effects as smoking the corresponding herb in a pipe."
    },
